    "texts": [
      {
        "level": 0,
        "text": "Some practical issues: Effect of NOISE\u000bCourtesy Juan Carlos Niebles and Ranjay Krishna"
      },
      {
        "level": 0,
        "text": "Consider a single row or column of the image"
      },
      {
        "level": 0,
        "text": "\u2013 Plotting intensity as a function of position gives a signal"
      },
      {
        "level": 0,
        "text": "\u2013 Where is the edge?"
